He gave you the courtesy of telling you he had to cancel (because sometimes shit comes up at the last minute) instead of just ghosting you, and you went off at him?

&#x200B;

Yeah, he ain't contacting you again, he's cut you off for being a psycho.

Combo units have two good points.  They take up less room, and they are set and forget.  You can chuck a load of washing into it in the morning, and when you get home from work, it will be clean and dry.

&#x200B;

They take a LOT longer though, and there's no lint filter, so you either have to run the tub clean cycle or wipe the lint out somehow.

